00:23:47.770 --> 00:23:53.230
10,000 human generations
of struggling and suffering

00:23:53.230 --> 00:23:56.260
and shivering and itching
and smelling horrible

00:23:56.260 --> 00:23:58.387
and being terrified
of saber-tooth tigers

00:23:58.387 --> 00:23:59.220
and everything else.

00:23:59.220 --> 00:24:02.111
And really, except
until very recently,

00:24:02.111 --> 00:24:03.610
