00:25:57.310 --> 00:25:58.450
I have magic.

00:25:58.450 --> 00:26:02.685
I have more magic in this pocket
than Merlin ever dreamed of.

00:26:02.685 --> 00:26:04.060
I have all the
world's knowledge,

00:26:04.060 --> 00:26:05.410
all the world's symphonies.

00:26:05.410 --> 00:26:08.590
