passengers when I was born,

00:26:19.080 --> 00:26:22.740
and there are 7.5 or 7.6
billion now-- triple.

00:26:22.740 --> 00:26:26.430
And I'm still, as you
can see, a young man.

00:26:26.430 --> 00:26:29.200
We really could,
between nuclear winter,

00:26:29.200 --> 00:26:31.740
which is not a good
solution to global warming,

00:26:31.740 --> 00:26:34.470
and bioterrorism
