00:49:15.100 --> 00:49:16.183
And that wasn't nefarious.

00:49:16.183 --> 00:49:19.220
That was just terrible.

00:49:19.220 --> 00:49:21.520
But when you have
the former KGB,

00:49:21.520 --> 00:49:23.050
when you have
thousands of agents

