00:49:27.959 --> 00:49:30.250
on our country to try to
destabilize our country, which

00:49:30.250 --> 00:49:35.350
is happening, and destabilize
the world, which is happening,

00:49:35.350 --> 00:49:36.942
I do take issue.

00:49:36.942 --> 00:49:38.650
I kind of understand
it, but I take issue

00:49:38.650 --> 00:49:40.960
with those of our talking
heads who go on TV

00:49:40.960 --> 00:49:42.130
and they say, now, I'm
not saying it would

00:49:42.130 --> 00:49:43.280
have changed the election.

00:49:43.280 --> 00:49:44.710
Well, of course it would
have changed the election.

00:49:44.710 --> 00:49:46.126
I mean, you couldn't
have gotten--

00:49:46.126 --> 00:49:48.010
77,000 votes didn't
happen because people

00:49:48.010 --> 00:49:53.170
reading Facebook fake stuff
from KGB kind of people.

00:49:53.170 --> 00:49:55.040
They're reading how
horrible Hillary is,

00:49:55.040 --> 00:49:56.720
and they're getting
