00:49:56.720 --> 00:49:58.954
I mean, you guys know
a lot more about how

00:49:58.954 --> 00:49:59.870
all these things work.

00:49:59.870 --> 00:50:04.220
But you do no evil, and Putin
is all about doing evil.

00:50:04.220 --> 00:50:07.400
So that was a huge
thing, I think.

00:50:07.400 --> 00:50:09.550
And then the last big piece--

00:50:09.550 --> 00:50:12.797
well, so the third one that's
smaller, but still very

00:50:12.797 --> 00:50:14.630
meaningful and a little
bit related to this,

00:50:14.630 --> 00:50:18.650
is the Comey stuff and the
way the media played it.

00:50:18.650 --> 00:50:22.717
This email thing is as big a
deal as Russia attacking us.

00:50:22.717 --> 00:50:24.050
These are two equivalent things.

00:50:24.050 --> 00:50:24.640
Each one is a scandal.

00:50:24.640 --> 00:50:25.730
We've got to be even handed.

00:50:25.730 --> 00:50:28.188
We don't want to lose readership
or whatever the reason is.

00:50:28.188 --> 00:50:30.070
And we want to have a dog fight.

00:50:30.070 --> 00:50:33.900
So the Comey stuff, I don't
think it was intentional,

00:50:33.900 --> 00:50:35.580
but it was a big problem.

00:50:35.580 --> 00:50:38.300
And then finally, I mean,
the basket of deplorables

00:50:38.300 --> 00:50:41.510
sitting eight feet from
me, that was kind of

00:50:41.510 --> 00:50:44.670
like the 47% comment
that Romney did.

00:50:44.670 --> 00:50:46.040
And Romney's not a--

00:50:46.040 --> 00:50:48.970
boy, if we could have
Romney instead of Trump,

00:50:48.970 --> 00:50:52.565
Romney is a smart,
sane guy who, you know,

00:50:52.565 --> 00:50:56.375
et cetera, et cetera, not
my first choice, but OK.

00:50:56.375 --> 00:50:58.250
Anyway, so those were
the things that did it.

00:50:58.250 --> 00:51:03.050
Now the party, one area that
Barack Obama was not great at,

00:51:03.050 --> 00:51:04.910
because he did have
a lot on his plate,

00:51:04.910 --> 00:51:08.120
and not everybody is perfect
in every way, and nobody

00:51:08.120 --> 00:51:13.970
that I know, is he didn't pay
too much attention to the DNC.

00:51:13.970 --> 00:51:17.360
And having a lovely woman,
who is a friend of mine

00:51:17.360 --> 00:51:19.310
and all that, Debbie
Wasserman Schultz,

00:51:19.310 --> 00:51:25.160
but having a part-time chair of
the party for four years, who

00:51:25.160 --> 00:51:29.630
also has a mother of
three, and was Congress,

