I mean, I tend to
get confrontational,

00:54:14.980 --> 00:54:18.130
and I get sarcastic, and all
the things you shouldn't get.

00:54:18.130 --> 00:54:21.230
But there's a guy named
Richard Viguerie who

00:54:21.230 --> 00:54:23.490
