conservative direct mail,

00:54:23.490 --> 00:54:25.170
and I've been going
to the same thing

00:54:25.170 --> 00:54:28.830
each year for like 30 years, I
think on Renaissance weekend.

00:54:28.830 --> 00:54:29.580
And I see Richard.

