00:54:55.680 --> 00:54:58.590
and what rights can we not have?

00:54:58.590 --> 00:55:01.250
And just tell us,
what do you think?

00:55:01.250 --> 00:55:02.920
Well, let me think about that.

00:55:02.920 --> 00:55:04.920
I'll talk to you next
year about it or whatever.

00:55:04.920 --> 00:55:07.830
And then next year came,
and he didn't talk about it.

00:55:07.830 --> 00:55:09.090
So the LGBT one--

00:55:09.090 --> 00:55:11.910
on the climate change,
you've got tribes.

