But we don't have to
get 100% of the vote.

00:55:19.062 --> 00:55:20.520
I mean, it would
be wonderful if we

00:55:20.520 --> 00:55:24.810
can change the educational
system and get more people to--

00:55:24.810 --> 00:55:28.270
and begin to-- it's
such a big topic,

00:55:28.270 --> 00:55:31.590
and obviously there
are no easy answers.

00:55:31.590 --> 00:55:33.510
But it is important
to realize that we

00:55:33.510 --> 00:55:37.050
haven't failed if we only
get more votes than they get.

00:55:39.570 --> 00:55:42.801
At least that gives us a
chance to have our agenda work,

00:55:42.801 --> 00:55:45.300
and give people health care,
and have them not want it taken

00:55:45.300 --> 00:55:47.510
away, and stuff like that.

00:55:47.510 --> 00:55:52.620
Anyway, you're great to come,
and thank you for Google.

00:55:52.620 --> 00:55:55.230
And it's a miracle, Google.

00:55:55.230 --> 00:55:57.509
I mean, it's totally
changed my life.

00:55:57.509 --> 00:55:59.050
I've been writing
about this forever.

00:55:59.050 --> 00:56:00.064
I mean, it's a miracle.

00:56:00.064 --> 00:56:01.980
I don't know how it
works, but it's a miracle.

00:56:01.980 --> 00:56:02.550
So thank you.

